'''Maurizio Lazzarato''' is a philosopher, expert on Gabriel Tarde, co-founder of the magazine [[Multitudes]], who has been specializing in the analysis of cognitive capitalism, and its discontents, hence his work on the P2P-concept of Multitudes, the coordination format in political and economic resistance, etc.. His work is historically situated in the Italian movement of 'autonomous Marxism'.


